# $Id$

PortSystem 1.0
PortGroup cmake 1.0

name                clog
version             1.2.1
categories          sysutils textproc
platforms           darwin
license             MIT
maintainers         raimue openmaintainer
description         A colorized log tail utility
long_description \
    Clog is a colorized log tail utility. It can spot patterns in an input \
    stream and colorize or suppress the lines. It can also decorate the lines \
    with time- or date-stamps.

homepage            http://tasktools.org/projects/clog.html
master_sites        http://tasktools.org/download/

checksums           rmd160  d49f820e1e25f4020c28de68c1440e32f6eea9aa \
                    sha256  880cfe248326a5c6f7c2a183008c76fae8b78c45f6e5795f74d02627e634f29d

livecheck.type      regex
livecheck.url       http://tasktools.org/
livecheck.regex     ${name}-(\\d(\\.\\d)+)\\.tar
